{"title":"Brompton’s new B75 folds up small but leaves your wallet large","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/26/brompton-b75-folding-bike/","date":1627313541000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span>Brompton’s new B75 folding bike is a great city companion for riders who want to take the guesswork out of daily commutes and save a few bucks while they’re at it.</span></p><p><span>In the past year, bicycles have seen a historic boom as people found themselves working from home, avoiding public transit and trying to find new ways to navigate the cities where they live.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x339/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" alt=\"Brompton B75 bike \" width=\"792\" height=\"554\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 792w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-297x208.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-120x84.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-768x537.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-696x487.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-600x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-100x70.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x339/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" ezoid=\"0.6255503008922509\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 792w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-297x208.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-120x84.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-768x537.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-696x487.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-600x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165733/brompton-b75-1_1-e1627312978577-100x70.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 100w\">But as workers get back to offices in urban centers, the challenges of bringing full-size bikes into the workplace, finding safe and adequate space to park them or dealing with unforeseen hiccups in daily schedules can make having a large bike to lug around a bit daunting.</span></p><h2>Enter The Brompton B75</h2><p><span>Brompton bills the <a href=\"https://us.brompton.com/catalogue/bikes/brompton-b75/brompton-b75\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">B75</a> as a take-anywhere, simple machine that offers flexibility and convenience for urban riders. The bike weighs 25 pounds and folds down to a compact 22.2 x 23 x 10.6, making it small enough to toss in the trunk of a car or even take on a plane.</span></p><p><span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634.jpg\" alt=\"Brompton B75 partially folded\" width=\"648\" height=\"428\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634.jpg 648w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-636x420.jpg 636w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634.jpg 648w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-297x196.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-120x79.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165704/brompton_b75_2_1_1-e1627313022634-636x420.jpg 636w\">London-based Brompton has been making folding bikes for more than 40 years. The company offers several foldable bike models, including Superlight and E-bike options ranging in price from about $1,500 to just more than $4,000.</span></p><p><span>At MSRP $1,095, the B75 is Brompton’s most inexpensive model. Its frame is composed of tough steel, and it comes with a simple, three-speed drivetrain geared for the city.</span></p><p><span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804.jpg\" alt=\"Brompton B75 folding bike closed\" width=\"580\" height=\"440\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804.jpg 580w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-297x225.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-120x91.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-554x420.jpg 554w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-80x60.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804.jpg 580w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-297x225.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-120x91.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-554x420.jpg 554w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165709/brompton_b75_3_1_1-e1627313050804-80x60.jpg 80w\"></span></p><p><span>It also can be fitted with racks, bags and mudguards to carry daily supplies and protect riders from getting dirty.</span></p><h2>The Virtues Of Folding Bikes</h2><p><span><a href=\"https://gearjunkie.com/biking/fastest-folding-bike-brompton-nyc-first-look-review\">Folding bikes</a> offer a simple solution to many of urban commuting’s major problems. Full-size bikes are tough to fit into elevators and in office spaces. Leaving them outside all day in the weather or where thieves can easily grab them can be an anxiety-inducing exercise that no one wants to add to their day.</span></p><p><span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462.jpg\" alt=\"three speed folding bike\" width=\"674\" height=\"480\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462.jpg 674w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-297x212.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-120x85.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-590x420.jpg 590w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-100x70.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 674px) 100vw, 674px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462.jpg 674w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-297x212.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-120x85.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-590x420.jpg 590w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/23165714/brompton_b75_8_1_1-e1627313087462-100x70.jpg 100w\">It’s also safe to say that no one wants to get stranded or drenched by unexpected storms in their work clothes because they don’t have a way to get their bike home without venturing out into the rain.</span></p><p><span>The Brompton B75 takes all that guesswork out of daily commutes, offering comfortable, efficient rides that break down to a size that can easily slide under a desk or be carried onto an elevator without generating angry glances and eye rolls.</span></p><p><span><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lWhGZtOKLYk?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\